  "prompt": "Which is a suitable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Upson County GA?",
  "response": "Finding a suitable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Upson County, GA, depends on your specific needs, such as treatment programs, insurance coverage, and amenities. Here are a few reputable rehab centers in the general vicinity:\n\n1. **Ridgeview Institute Monroe** (Monroe, GA)  \n   - Located about 1.5 hours from Upson County, Ridgeview offers comprehensive inpatient treatment for substance abuse and co-occurring mental health disorders.  \n   - Website: [ridgeviewinstitute.com](https://www.ridgeviewinstitute.com)  \n   - Phone: (770) 534-3426  \n\n2. **Laurel Heights Hospital** (Atlanta, GA)  \n   - About 1.5\u20132 hours from Upson County, Laurel Heights provides inpatient addiction treatment for adults and adolescents.  \n   - Website: [laurelheightshospital.com](https://www.laurelheightshospital.com)  \n   - Phone: (770) 491-1885  \n\n3. **Willowbrooke at Tanner** (Villa Rica, GA)  \n   - Approximately 1.5 hours from Upson County, this facility offers inpatient mental health and addiction treatment programs.  \n   - Website: [tanner.org/willowbrooke](https://www.tanner.org/willowbrooke)  \n   - Phone: (770) 812-3226  \n\n4. **RiverEdge Behavior Health** (Macon, GA)  \n   - Located about 1 hour from Upson County, RiverEdge provides inpatient detox and substance abuse treatment.  \n   - Website: [riveredge.org](https://www.riveredge.org)  \n   - Phone: (478) 803-7600  \n\n5. **Talbot Recovery Campus** (Atlanta, GA)  \n   - About 1.5\u20132 hours from Upson County, Talbot offers inpatient and outpatient addiction treatment services.  \n   - Website: [talbotrecovery.org](https://www.talbotrecovery.org)  \n   - Phone: (678) 815-8258  \n\nBefore choosing a facility, contact them directly to verify availability, insurance acceptance, and specific treatment options. You can also reach out to SAMHSA\u2019s National Helpline at **1-800-662-HELP (4357)** for assistance in finding a rehab center that meets your needs.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
